snippet.title: Cats vs Aliens Official Gameplay Teaser - A Cat-tastic Cozy Survivorslike
snippet.description:
My cat-themed attempt at creating a half cozy crafty, half bullet heaven game is getting closer to demo ready every day!  The next playtesting phase starts January 10th, 2025!  Sign up directly on Steam to participate (and wishlist the game while you're there!)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2896390/Cats_vs_Aliens/

Music by Isaac Lawrence
